divs: Sighting Detailsat the time i was 1 block east of the fox river looking northeast towards the city of bartlet waching the commercial on there final approach to ohara field. i obsevred an object that first thought to be a high flying bird. i then saw the object move around and above the jet in short right hand turns. it then moved to straight east of me,made some irregular moves. then it went straight south towards aurora at a very high rate of speed. at all times it made no sound. no bird can move like this. i cannot explain what saw, but it makes no sense what it was. this also was seen by my son who standing with me
